          <text><![CDATA[<p>This bill amends the Internal Revenue Code, with respect to the taxation of S corporations, to exclude from the 100 shareholder limitation for such corporations individuals who acquired shares in an S corporation through: (1) a small issues public offering, or (2) one or more crowdfunding offerings. </p>]]></text>
          <updateDate>2016-03-22T04:00:00Z</updateDate>
          <name>Introduced in House</name>
        </item>
      </billSummaries>
